db & Migration
--------------

rake db:drop                                    => Drop all tables
rake db:migrate                                 => Create table as per migration script
rake db:rollback                                => Rollback last migration
rails generate migration <migration_file_name>  => Generate migration script
rake db:seed                                    => Execute db/seed.rb
rake db:reset                                   => Recreated dB with all migrations

Code Generation
---------------

rails new <my_rails_app>                        => Generates new Rails app under folder <my_rails_app>/

rails generate controller <my_cont>             => Generates <my_cont>_controller.rb abd Tests (can be used with several arguments)

rails generate scaffold Product \               => Generates Model/View/Controller/Helper/Migration/Tests for Product
title:string \
description:text \
image_url:string price:decimal

Info
----

rake routes                                     => Info of the routes generated/used

Testing
-------

rake test                                       => Runs all unit, functional and integration tests.
rake test:units                                 => Runs all the unit tests.
rake test:functionals                           => Runs all the functional tests.
rake test:integration                           => Runs all the integration tests.

Server
------

rails server


